name: FINU
public_notice: Formula Inu (FINU) has rebranded to FINU (FINU). For detailed information, kindly visit this post on Twitter.
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

The following token has a variable tax function on the smart contract to change tax rates post deployment.
Do your own research and be careful if you are trading this token.

description.en: Formula Inu is a Decentralized Finance (DeFi) project on the Ethereum Blockchain. We fill the gap between the racing industry and web3. We are creating an ecosystem of multiple revenue streams generated from in-real-life and web3 business operations. Profits generated from our business operations revenue streams will be allocated to our holders via stablecoin-rewards, as well as to further develop and market the overall project operations.
